Dependencies
------------
 - libgtk-3.0-dev
 - libgtksourceview-3.0-dev
 - libgranite
 - libgconf-2.0-dev


Testing and installation
------------------------
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..
$ make
$ sudo make install # do not worry, it's only needed for gsettings schema
$ ./scratch

Thanks!